hanzo-cubecl-hip-sys
====================

This crate is a fork of `cubecl-hip-sys` 7.2.5321100 by Tracel Technologies Inc.
(https://github.com/tracel-ai/cubecl-hip), redistributed under its original
MIT OR Apache-2.0 license (see LICENSE-MIT and LICENSE-APACHE).

Modification by Hanzo AI, Inc.:
  * build.rs (`set_hip_feature`): when the system HIP patch version is NEWER
    than any bindings this crate ships (e.g. ROCm 7.13 reports HIP patch 99004,
    past the newest shipped 53211), select the latest available bindings instead
    of emitting an undefined `hip_<patch>` feature. ABI-safe: AMD versions every
    changed symbol (the R0600 revisions) and ROCm 7.13's headers still map the
    wrapped symbols to their R0600 revision, so the latest bindings link against
    the newer runtime unchanged.
  * src/hipconfig.rs: added the helper functions the fallback needs
    (`extract_latest_hip_feature_from_path`, `extract_latest_hip_feature_from_contents`,
    `hip_feature_available`) with unit tests.

All other files are verbatim from upstream. No upstream authorship is claimed.

